面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，到我們的網站        <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCIuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=c351dae0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>              。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"ba913fe8c936cb7b713f801fce5780933f6b1ca3","tid":2121232,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T07:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfcbe47e9d2255144765179605b5662976ce75df","tid":2121232,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T07:42:45.000Z","msg":"最後冇69互含真係曬咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8bf2dd153cabdd7d6ff79dbde0ec3950ba8807b","tid":2121232,"uid":211729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T07:48:41.000Z","msg":"呢到唔是講估台"},{"pid":"8580d0c4e9af7c1cb7b343902a722c970b471dff","tid":2121232,"uid":259499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T07:55:41.000Z","msg":"真定假都好，故事係感人"},{"pid":"cd54c1de7431ba44973da48b5a00b4a7140c28e9","tid":2121232,"uid":203701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T09:46:07.000Z","msg":"希望係假"},{"pid":"ec5c5869c116489c3ae28cf2772eea59a7d0a0da","tid":2121232,"uid":311330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T17:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}